{"tid":1893613,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)無敵破壞王1-2 監獄格鬥4>2>3","createTime":"2020-02-23T11:26:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-23T19:56:02.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c6c25017ec4203e8faaec074a86d14c853ea0a21","tid":1893613,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T11:26:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">新沙士已經殺到黎 自己注意身體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=c0FEOXRBadflfKsXjMdAytjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=94707046\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER 無CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=c0FEOXRBadflfKsXjMdAytjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=024f3ddf\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得返OK台(自己按播放制) 有CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=c0FEOXRBadflfKsXjMdAytjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=6f742642\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;&lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn1.thr.com/sites/default/files/imagecache/scale_crop_768_433/2018/11/ralph_breaks_the_internet_still_8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.thr.com%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fimagecache%2Fscale_crop_768_433%2F2018%2F11%2Fralph_breaks_the_internet_still_8.jpg&h=c0c33406&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://outalpha.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/CZvKWAKWwAEQcAt-e1472162325808.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Foutalpha.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F08%2FCZvKWAKWwAEQcAt-e1472162325808.jpg&h=47f076bf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/88/1b/e6/881be6155294dff3b41fc98dd1220837.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2F88%2F1b%2Fe6%2F881be6155294dff3b41fc98dd1220837.jpg&h=560d881c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.「無敵破壞王」（Wreck-It Ralph）生活在一個1980年代出品的電子遊戲《修繕王阿修》（Fix-It Felix, Jr.）中。他的身分是每天在遊戲中的好人公寓大搞破壞的一個反派角色，修繕王阿修（Fix-It Felix）則是由玩家操作，及時趕到進行修補的英雄人物，阿修贏得許多獎牌並包攬一切榮耀。日復一日，破壞王雷夫漸漸厭倦了自己作為反派的生活，看到阿修被勝利的光環所圍繞，自己卻只能在孤單地生活在遊戲裡的垃圾堆角落中，讓他感到非常不是滋味。某天在30周年的派對上與好人公寓的房東老金起爭執之後，決定賭一口氣..<br />\n<br />\n2.消滅渦輪六年後，破壞王雷夫和雲妮露&middot;凡史威茲一直是好朋友，每天完成立瓦親子遊樂場（Litwak's Family Fun Center and Arcade）的工作後，晚上兩人會出去散心。然而，在賽車遊戲《甜蜜衝刺》（Sugar Rush）當了六年賽車手的雲妮露早就厭倦了毫無變化的賽道，所以雷夫突發奇想，給雲妮露開了一條隱藏賽道。對於這條賽道，雲妮露很享受，然而它造成遊戲脫離了玩家控制，街機上的方向盤被卡住，玩家不小心折斷了方向盤。立瓦想把方向盤重新接上，不料將其弄斷。得知遊戲廠商已經倒閉多年，立瓦別無選擇，只能忍痛將《甜蜜衝刺》的電源拔掉，雲妮露和遊戲中的角色成了無業遊民<br />\n<br />\n3.犯人戰士尤裏?伯伊卡（斯科特阿金斯 飾）霸氣回歸!依然要參加格鬥賽!然而這一部裏，當他把對手解決掉後，對手意外死亡，這也讓他重新審視自己參賽的意義，尤其發現遺孀被幕後黑手控制，他要爲她的自由而戰!不過這次的對手更難對付了!<br />\n<br />\n4.故事敘述在前集過後的數年，前世界重量級拳王喬治&middot;「冰人」&middot;錢伯為了在退休時間賺點錢，便而前往俄羅斯拍廣告。在造訪當地進行的一系列的拳擊比賽時，他遭他人誣陷持有古柯鹼，而再度被送往監獄，但那裡的氣候卻比以前待的監獄還要寒冷。<br />\n在那他發現了該監獄官員安排的非法綜合格鬥賽，以助在外的大亨賺取賭金。為此，冰人與背後的大亨達成協議，只要打倒獄中最強的戰士尤里&middot;波卡就能重獲自由..<br />\n<br />\n5.故事敘述繼前集的數年過後，右膝受傷的失去戰力的尤里&middot;波卡因自卑而引退，而改至廁所打掃。但因黑幫老大兼監獄格鬥的大亨嘎卡的緣故，使得尤里再次復出參戰。後來，尤里被轉送往喬治亞；在那，他除了面對喜歡碎碎念並與自己不合的美國人托波外，還要和來自他國的囚犯們展開廝殺..<br />\n<br />\n7 30PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=c0FEOXRBadflfKsXjMdAytjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=71a13d4a\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=c0FEOXRBadflfKsXjMdAytjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=c79847f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e399b915982bcf0f4f3bc343addff62f9a55252b","tid":1893613,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T11:28:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d28747380c3c627326d006222de1eb7a20ad6fcc","tid":1893613,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T12:04:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30622beeee7fad1b89520c9aa386ec7df3c91682","tid":1893613,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T13:07:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea36456d9101dce54899cfcd7b2f8f2d24ce6cc7","tid":1893613,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T16:07:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac2d9eb0508c83156b5c097d27301c5f3c2285ee","tid":189